snippet.textDisplay:
So I have watched doctors presenting their facts, the W.H.O, virology experts, international virology experts, Coronavirus in particular experts, and Canada experts etc. And this is what most experts (not Canadian) have said:
1. Up to 14 days you are contagious even though you do not know you are incubating the virus
2. The virus can live on solid surfaces for up to 6 days
3. The virus can infect through all mucus membranes; such as the eye, nose and mouth
4. A cab driver became infected transporting travellers to airport
5. Two German individuals became infected when a lecturer at event was unknowingly infected
6. In just one month the CONFIRMED infected has doubled the amount of people infected from SARS
7. Over 300 flights coming out of China to varying areas of the globe before the quarantine was established in Wuhan
8. An entire city Wuhan, 10 million population, was quarantined with most confined to their homes. Police guard the entrances to the city.
9. The Canadian experts have downplayed and have not conveyed the TRUTH
10. SARS only had a 3-5 day incubation and no contagiousness during that period...contagiousness from SARS reached its peak 14 days into symptoms.
11. Many unknowns still exist.....this is a new virus that does not even have an official name yet.....they (experts outside of Canada) are afraid of mutating and further transmissibility by unknown means.
12. Just because you are Chinese, or other East and south east Asians ....does not mean you are infected. Many people of diverse ethnicities travel to parts of China for business or pleasure so keep this in mind.

Our government in Canada and the media has displayed irresponsibility in conveying the truth and in arrogance. If this disease is spread in Canada, it is because of our leaders have abused their authority in their neglect of being proactive in securing the safety of the vulnerable in our society. When you use blanket-like statements like "we are well prepared because of SARS"......a completely different virus that was only transmissible after incubation.
Oh Canada ....shame sham Oh Canada.

10.  SARS only had a 3-5 day incubation and no contagiousness during that period...contagiousness from SARS reached its peak 14 days into symptoms.

12.  Just because you are Chinese, or other East and south east Asians ....does not mean you are infected.  Many people of diverse ethnicities travel to parts of China for business or pleasure so keep this in mind.  

Our government in Canada and the media has displayed irresponsibility in conveying the truth and in arrogance.  If this disease is spread in Canada, it is because of our leaders have abused their authority in their neglect of being proactive in securing the safety of the vulnerable in our society.  When you use blanket-like statements like "we are well prepared because of SARS"......a completely different virus that was only transmissible after incubation.
Oh Canada ....shame sham Oh Canada.
